      "description": "Optional, tint multiplied to the color. Tint method logic varies, but often refers to the \"rain\" and \"temperature\" of the biome the block is placed in to compute the tint. Supported tint methods are \"none\", \"default_foliage\", \"birch_foliage\", \"evergreen_foliage\", \"dry_foliage\", \"grass\" and \"water\"",
      "title": "Tint Method"
